#. Used as HTML title of the page
#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:6
msgid "Web Literacy: Vital to Internet Health"
msgstr "Llythrennedd Gwe: Yn Hanfodol i Iechyd y Rhyngrwyd"

#. Used as HTML description of the page
#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:11
msgid ""
"Web literacy means having the skills to read, write, and participate online. "
"A healthy internet is yours to master."
msgstr ""
"Mae llythrennedd y We'n golygu cael sgiliau i ddarllen, ysgrifennu a chymryd "
"rhan ar-lein. Mae rhyngrwyd iach ar gael ei chi i'w feistroli."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:15
msgid "Privacy &amp; Security"
msgstr "Preifatrwydd a Diogelwch"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:19
msgid "Open Innovation"
msgstr "Arloesi Agored"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:23
msgid "Decentralization"
msgstr "Datganoli"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:27
msgid "Digital Inclusion"
msgstr "Cynhwysiad Digidol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:31
msgid "Web Literacy"
msgstr "Llythrennedd Gwe"

#. Used as Page Title
#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:36
msgid "A healthy Internet means everyone has the skills to thrive"
msgstr "Mae rhyngrwyd iach yn golygu fod gan bawb y sgiliau i ffynnu"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:40
msgid ""
"People everywhere should have the knowledge they need to tap into the full "
"power of the Internet – and use it to make their lives and the world better. "
"This means everyone needs to be able to read, write, and participate online."
msgstr ""
"Dylai fod gan bawb ymhob man yr wybodaeth angenrheidiol i gysylltu â phŵer "
"llawn y Rhyngrwyd – ac i'w ddefnyddio i wella eu bywyd a'r byd. Mae hy yn "
"golygu fod angen i bawb fod a'r gallu i ddarllen, ysgrifennu a chymryd rhan "
"ar-lein."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:44
msgid "A healthy Internet is yours to master."
msgstr "Mae rhyngrwyd iach yna i chi ei feistroli."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:48
msgid "Here are three areas where we can make a difference."
msgstr "Dyma dri maes lle gallwn ni wneud gwahaniaeth."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:52
msgid "Making Web Literacy Meaningful"
msgstr "Gwneud Llythrennedd y We'n Ystyrlon"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:56
msgid "Teaching Web Literacy Effectively"
msgstr "Dysgu Llythrennedd y We'n Effeithiol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:60
msgid "Cultivating Digital Citizenship"
msgstr "Meithrin Dinasyddiaeth Ddigidol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:64
msgid "Making Web literacy meaningful for everyone"
msgstr "Gwneud llythrennedd Gwe'n ystyrlon i bawb"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:68
msgid ""
"Web literacy should mean all the skills we need to think, create, and thrive "
"online."
msgstr ""
"Dylai llythrennedd y We feddwl yr holl sgiliau sydd eu hangen ar gyfer "
"meddwl, creu a ffynnu ar-lein."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:72
msgid ""
"Many people hear the term Web literacy and think it means learning to code, "
"or <abbr>STEM</abbr> (science, technology, engineering, math) education. But "
"Web literacy is much broader than that – it should include all the skills to "
"be confident and competent online. To be empowered digital citizens, we all "
"need to know how to navigate, how to share, what information to trust, and "
"most importantly, how to expand the frontiers of our knowledge."
msgstr ""
"Mae llawer o bobl sy'n clywed y term llythrennedd gwe'n meddwl ei fod yn "
"golygu dysgu codio neu addysg <abbr>STEM</abbr> (gwyddoniaeth, technoleg, "
"peirianneg a mathemateg). Ond mae llythrennedd Gwe'n fwy na hynny – dylai "
"gynnwys yr holl sgiliau i fod yn hyderus a chymwys ar-lein. I fod yn "
"ddinesydd digidol grymus, mae angen i ni wybod sut i symud, sut i rannu, pa "
"wybodaeth gallwn ymddiried ynddo, ac yn fwy pwysig, sut i ehangu ffiniau ein "
"gwybodaeth."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:76
msgid ""
"82% of American middle-schoolers assessed couldn’t tell the difference "
"between an ad labeled “sponsored content” and a real news story on a website."
msgstr ""
"Mewn asesiad o ddisgyblion ysgolion uwchradd yn yr Unol Daleithiau doedd 82% "
"ddim yn gallu dweud y gwahaniaeth rhwng hysbyseb wedi ei labeli “cynnwys "
"wedi ei noddi” a stori newyddion go iawn ar wefan."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:80
msgid "Source: <a href=\"%(stanford)s\">Stanford University</a>"
msgstr "Ffynhonnell: <a href=\"%(stanford)s\">Stanford University</a>"

#. This is used as a decorative element in a callout box.
#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:85
msgid "82%"
msgstr "82%"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:89
msgid "How you can develop meaningful Web literacy"
msgstr "Sut mae modd datblygu llythrennedd Gwe ystyrlon"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:93
msgid "Learn to spot fake news"
msgstr "Dysgu adnabod newyddion ffug"

#. ifla.org refers to The International Federation of Library Associations and Institutions. Currently the site is available in English, German and Spanish.
#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:98
msgid ""
"Take a <a href=\"%(quiz)s\">fake news quiz</a>, or <a href=\"%(primer)s"
"\">follow this helpful primer</a> from our friends at the <abbr title="
"\"International Federation of Library Associations and Institutions\">IFLA</"
"abbr>."
msgstr ""
"Cymrwch <a href=\"%(quiz)s\">gwis newyddion ffug</a>, neu <a href="
"\"%(primer)s\">ddilyn y canllaw defnyddiol hwn </a> gan ein ffrindiau yn yr "
"<abbr title=\"International Federation of Library Associations and "
"Institutions\">IFLA</abbr>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:102
msgid "Tinker with X-Ray Goggles"
msgstr "Chwarae gyda X-Ray Goggles"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:106
msgid ""
"See and remix the code on your favorite Web pages with <a href=\"%(goggles)s"
"\">this fun Mozilla tool</a>."
msgstr ""
"Gweld ac ailgymysgu'r cod ar eich hoff dudalennau Gwe gyda <a href="
"\"%(goggles)s\">teclyn hwyl yma gan Mozilla</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:110
msgid "Join the club"
msgstr "Ymuno â'r clwb"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:114
msgid ""
"Join or start <a href=\"%(clubs)s\">your local Mozilla club</a> to learn the "
"Web among your peers."
msgstr "Ymuno neu gychwyn <a href=\"%(clubs)s\">eich clwb Mozilla lleol</a>"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:118
msgid "How Mozilla is making Web literacy meaningful for everyone"
msgstr "Sut mae Mozilla'n gwneud llythrennedd Gwe'n ystyrlon i bawb"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:122
msgid "Defining the term"
msgstr "Diffinio'r term"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:126
msgid ""
"Collaborating with leaders in the field to create Mozilla’s <a href=\"%(map)s"
"\">Web Literacy Map</a> that provides a clear, practical definition of web "
"literacy."
msgstr ""
"Creu <a href=\"%(map)s\">Map Llythrennedd Gwe</a> ar y cyd gydag arweinwyr "
"yn y maes, sy'n darparu diffiniad ymarferol a chlir o lythrennedd gwe."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:130
msgid "Advocating for education policy"
msgstr "Eirioli dros bolisi addysg"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:134
msgid ""
"Working with educations and policymakers to help make Web literacy <a href="
"\"%(education)s\">as foundational to education as reading and math</a>."
msgstr ""
"Gweithio gydag addysgwyr a swyddogion polisi i'w cynorthwyo i wneud "
"llythrennedd Gwe <a href=\"%(education)s\">mor sylfaenol i addysg ag yw "
"darllen a mathemateg</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:138
msgid "Teaching Web literacy effectively"
msgstr "Dysgu llythrennedd Gwe yn effeithiol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:142
msgid ""
"Web literacy should be as foundational to education as reading, writing, and "
"math – and it should be taught everywhere learning happens."
msgstr ""
"Dylai llythrennedd Gwe fod mor sylfaenol i addysg ag yw darllen, ysgrifennu "
"a mathemateg – a dylai gael ei ddysgu ymhob man lle mae addysgu'n digwydd."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:146
msgid ""
"Learning Web literacy is like any other essential skill: we learn best by "
"doing. And in the digital world, learning happens not just with teachers in "
"the classroom, but everywhere there’s an Internet connection. We need all "
"kinds of educators to have the knowledge and resources to teach Web literacy "
"the way kids learn it best. And we need to make sure every student grows up "
"not just on the Web, but fluent in the way it works."
msgstr ""
"Mae dysgu llythrennedd Gwe yn debyg i unrhyw sgil hanfodol arall: rydym yn "
"dysgu orau drwy wneud. Ac mewn byd digidol, mae dysgu'n digwydd nid dim ond "
"gydag athrawon yn y dosbarth ond ymhob man lle mae yna gysylltiad Rhyngrwyd. "
"Mae angen arnom i bob math o addysgwyr i gael y wybodaeth a'r adnoddau i "
"ddysgu llythrennedd Gwe yn ôl fel mae plant yn ei ddysgu orau. Ac rydym "
"angen gwneud yn siŵr fod pob myfyriwr nid dim ond ar y We, ond yn hyddysg yn "
"y ffordd mae'n gweithio."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:150
msgid ""
"Increasing the number of young adults with Internet skills is a United "
"Nations Sustainable Development Goal, and the UN now tracks schools with "
"computers and Internet."
msgstr ""
"Mae cynyddu'r nifer o oedolion ifanc sydd â sgiliau'r Rhyngrwyd yn United "
"Nations Sustainable Development Goal ac mae'r UN yn tracio ysgolion sydd â "
"chyfrifiaduron a'r Rhyngrwyd."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:154
msgid "Source: <a href=\"%(itu)s\">ITU</a>"
msgstr "Ffynhonnell: <a href=\"%(itu)s\">ITU</a>"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:158
msgid "How you can teach Web literacy"
msgstr "Sut i ddysgu llythrennedd Gwe"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:162
msgid "Become a Web teacher"
msgstr "Beth am fod yn athro Gwe?"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:166
msgid ""
"Use <a href=\"%(activities)s\">these activities and instructions</a> to help "
"your kids and your community build strong Web literacy skills."
msgstr ""
"Defnyddiwch <a href=\"%(activities)s\">y gweithgareddau a'r cyfarwyddid hyn</"
"a> i helpu eich plant a'ch cymuned i adeiladu sgiliau Rhyngrwyd cryf."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:170
msgid "Ask for it"
msgstr "Gofynnwch amdano"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:174
msgid ""
"Tell your school – and those of your kids – that Web literacy is essential "
"to education, and should go beyond having computers in the classroom."
msgstr ""
"Dywedwch wrth eich ysgol – ac ysgol eich plant – fod llythrennedd gwe'n "
"hanfodol i addysg a dylai fynd tu hwnt i fod â chyfrifiaduron yn y dosbarth."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:178
msgid "How Mozilla is teaching Web literacy"
msgstr "Sut mae Mozilla'n addysgu llythrennedd gwe"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:182
msgid "Supporting teachers"
msgstr "Cefnogi athrawon"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:186
msgid ""
"Giving educators of all kinds the <a href=\"%(activities)s\">skills and "
"tools</a> they need to teach Web literacy, including knowledge-sharing "
"efforts like <a href=\"%(hive)s\">Hive Learning Networks</a>."
msgstr ""
"Yn rhoi i addysgwyr o bob math y <a href=\"%(activities)s\">sgiliau a'r "
"offer</a> sydd ei angen arnyn nhw i ddysgu llythrennedd Gwe, gan gynnwys "
"ymdrechion rhannu gwybodaeth fel yr <a href=\"%(hive)s\">Hive Learning "
"Networks</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:190
msgid "Supporting youth"
msgstr "Cefnogi pobl ifanc"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:194
msgid ""
"Creating opportunities and building communities to support youth accessing "
"the Web and <a href=\"%(learning)s\">learning how to use it</a>, like our <a "
"href=\"%(un_women)s\">partnership with UN Women</a> to teach digital skills "
"to girls and women in Africa."
msgstr ""
"Creu cyfleoedd ac adeiladu cymunedau i gefnogi pobl ifanc sy'n cael mynediad "
"i'r We ac yn <a href=\"%(learning)s\">dysgu sut i'w ddefnyddio</a>, fel ein "
"<a href=\"%(un_women)s\">partneriaeth gyda'r UN Women</a> er mwyn dysgu "
"sgiliau i ferched yn Affrica."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:198
msgid "Cultivating digital citizenship"
msgstr "Datblygu dinasyddiaeth ddigidol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:202
msgid ""
"A fundamental part of Web literacy is understanding the forces that shape "
"our lives online: the companies building our experiences, the politicians "
"crafting and supporting government policies, and the power we hold as "
"digital citizens to create the Internet we want. Having a say in our shared "
"future on the Web means deciding which values are most important to us, and "
"standing up for those values when they are threatened."
msgstr ""
"Rhan sylfaenol o lythrennedd Gwe yw deall y grymoedd sy'n siapio ein bywydau "
"ar-lein: y cwmnïau sy'n adeiladu ein profiadau, y gwleidyddion sy'n llunio a "
"chefnogi polisïau llywodraethol a'r grym sydd yn ein dwylo fel dinasyddion "
"digidol i greu'r Rhyngrwyd rydym ei eisiau. Mae cael llais yn y dyfodol "
"rydym yn ei rannu ar y We yn golygu penderfynu ar y gwerthoedd sydd mwyaf "
"pwysig i ni a chefnogi'r gwerthoedd hynny pan fyddant o dan fygythiad."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:206
msgid ""
"Indian Citizens sent over 750,000 emails to the Telecom Authority of India "
"in just one week, ultimately influencing their government’s decision to ban "
"discriminatory pricing practices."
msgstr ""
"Anfonodd Dinasyddion yr India 750,000 e-bost at y Telecom Authority of India "
"mewn un wythnos gan ddylanwadu yn y pen draw benderfyniad eu llywodraeth i "
"atal arferion prisio gwahaniaethol."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:210
msgid "Source: <a href=\"%(motherboard)s\">Motherboard</a>"
msgstr "Ffynhonnell: <a href=\"%(motherboard)s\">Motherboard</a>"

#. This is used as a decorative element in a callout box. Keep it short.
#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:215
msgid "750K"
msgstr "750K"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:219
msgid "How you can cultivate your digital citizenship"
msgstr "Sut fedrwch chi feithrin eich dinasyddiaeth ddigidol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:223
msgid "Get informed"
msgstr "Mynnwch wybod"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:227
msgid ""
"Which aspect of your online life matters most to you? <a href=\"%(privacy)s"
"\">Privacy</a>? Net neutrality? <a href=\"%(inclusion)s\">Inclusion</a>? "
"Learn about the issues, and find your own way to take action."
msgstr ""
"Pa agwedd o'ch bywyd ar-lein sydd fwyaf pwysig i chi?<a href=\"%(privacy)s"
"\">Preifatrwydd</a>? Niwtraliaeth y Rhyngrwyd?<a href=\"%(inclusion)s"
"\">Cynhwysiad</a>? Dysgwch am y materion hyn a dod o hyd i'ch ffordd eich "
"hun o weithredu."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:231
msgid "How Mozilla is cultivating digital citizenship"
msgstr "Sut mae Mozilla'n meithrin dinasyddiaeth ddigidol"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:235
msgid "Raising awareness"
msgstr "Codi ymwybyddiaeth"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:239
msgid ""
"Creating space for understanding, conversation, and community around what "
"makes a healthy Internet – like the page you’re reading right now, and "
"campaigns such as <a href=\"%(reform_copyright)s\">Reform Copyright</a>."
msgstr ""
"Creu gofod ar gyfer deall, sgwrsio a chymuned o amgylch yrn hyn sy'n creu "
"Rhyngrwyd iach – fel y dudalen rydych yn ei darllen ar hyn o bryd ac "
"ymgyrchoedd fel<a href=\"%(reform_copyright)s\">Diwygio Hawlfraint</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:243
msgid "Educating legislators"
msgstr "Addysgu Aelodau Cynulliad a'r Senedd"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:247
msgid ""
"<a href=\"%(advocating)s\">Advocating at the policy level</a> to make sure "
"politicians understand the role that digital citizens play in our society, "
"and adopt policies to empower citizens."
msgstr ""
"<a href=\"%(advocating)s\">Eirioli ar lefel polisi</a> i wneud yn siŵr fod "
"gwleidyddion yn deall y rôl mae dinasyddion digidol yn ei chwarae yn ein "
"cymdeithas a mabwysiadu polisïau sy'n grymuso dinasyddion."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:251
msgid "Hungry for more?"
msgstr "Eisiau gwybod rhagor?"

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:255
msgid ""
"Read on about Web Literacy in our <a href=\"%(healthreport)s\">Internet "
"Health Report</a>."
msgstr ""
"Rhagor am Arloesi Agored yn ein <a href=\"%(healthreport)s\">Internet Health "
"Report</a>."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:259
msgid "Stay informed."
msgstr "Derbyn gwybodaeth."

#: mozorg/internet-health/web-literacy.lang:263
msgid ""
"Sign up. Read up. Get the Mozilla newsletter to stay smart on the issues "
"affecting your life online."
msgstr ""
"Ymunwch. Darllenwch. Gallwch dderbyn cylchlythyr Mozilla er mwyn deall yn "
"well am faterion sy'n effeithio ar eich bywyd ar-lein."
